{"tid":2363795,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] End-to-end Encryption唔代表Facebook睇唔到你信息","createTime":"2021-01-12T13:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T07:45:39.000Z","uid":132326,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29f9ce8e98d12549c165887ae418346cd4a2e26e","tid":2363795,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"HTTPS就係用緊End-to-end Encryption，最大作用係防止傳輸途中有人偷睇(Eavesdrop)信息<br />\n<br />\n個原理係每個人各自有一個用嚟畀對方加密嘅public key同畀自己解密嘅private key<br />\n<br />\nA想send個信息畀B就會用B嘅public key加密再send畀B<br />\n<br />\nB收到密文就可以用B嘅private key解密<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁照計Facebook作為中間人應該睇唔到A畀B嘅信息？</strong><br />\n呢個就要視乎個App點處理你嘅信息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果個app純粹將一條信息由A send畀B，然後係A主動喺個app外面加密，先用個app send畀B，然後B再喺個app以外解密，咁個app係真係冇可能睇到你send緊乜。<br />\n<br />\n然後你問吓你自己：send message畀人個陣係你自己加密定交畀WhatsApp加密？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你打字係直接喺WhatsApp入面輸入，理論上WhatsApp係睇到你嘅信息！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁點解Signal同Telegram會比WhatsApp安全呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n咁就正如上面講過，係關乎個App點樣處理你嘅信息。Signal同Telegram都係open-source，你可以睇到佢會唔會靜靜雞同第三者透露咗咩資料！<br />\n<br />\n基本上可以講，所有唔係open-source嘅軟件都唔係最安全，你只可以信個開發商因為驚俾人告而唔做啲古靈精怪嘢。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook呢間公司專賣用戶私隱賺錢，我就唔多信喇，你要信都冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記住Facebook嘅客人係廣告商（或者想要你私隱嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯⋯港共？中共？），你至係佢件貨！"},{"pid":"7362c4281ace649fbb10c925ba5a41f1150e665d","tid":2363795,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d618e669400879e53edb7e5ea1529ee5c46d7","tid":2363795,"uid":21699,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T21:32:35.000Z","msg":"簡單講，whatsapp 可以喺你禁 send 之前果一下，偷偷地copy左你個 message先，然後先幫你加密send比對方。<br />\n<br />\n而signal同tg 因為係open-source，如果佢地有咁樣做，係會比人code review check到。但whatsapp唔係open-source，有冇咁做我地唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb44e405d7c24980477c24197613a74ee25b9541","tid":2363795,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果open source軟件，compile出嚟上架個binary，並唔係等於佢公開個嘅source，例如換咗某個加料file先compile，我哋點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e0e2fea7890a8be6acd59b4b452a2b427bdf69","tid":2363795,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb44e405d7c24980477c24197613a74ee25b9541","tid":2363795,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果open source軟件，compile出嚟上架個binary，並唔係等於佢公開個嘅source，例如換咗某個加料file先compile，我哋點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"可以對hash"},{"pid":"b386c1b161c1cc2dbfc4bdb1525dfde52e4a54eb","tid":2363795,"uid":279606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14e0e2fea7890a8be6acd59b4b452a2b427bdf69","tid":2363795,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb44e405d7c24980477c24197613a74ee25b9541","tid":2363795,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"咁如果open source軟件，compile出嚟上架個binary，並唔係等於佢公開個嘅source，例如換咗某個加料file先compile，我哋點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"可以對hash"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"hash可以撞 所以係咩類型嘅hash"},{"pid":"520346c690f155e287065509c3a43f4564aff899","tid":2363795,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b386c1b161c1cc2dbfc4bdb1525dfde52e4a54eb","tid":2363795,"uid":279606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14e0e2fea7890a8be6acd59b4b452a2b427bdf69","tid":2363795,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb44e405d7